N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 21 ยง 1261.12 - Permission required for aircraft to cross highways under own power or in tow

State Regulations

No aircraft shall cross an air terminal highway or a
public highway at an air terminal under its own power or under tow without
permission. Notes
